{"ops":[{"insert":"基本用途"},{"attributes":{"header":1},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"\n这是一个用于在表格或其他容器中展示字符串标签列表。当标签数量过多导致一行无法完整显示时，该组件会自动处理溢出情况，显示省略号和\"更多\"按钮。\n\n主要功能"},{"attributes":{"header":1},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"\n1. 标签展示：以行的形式展示字符串标签列表\n2. 溢出处理：当标签无法在一行内完整显示时：\n   - 显示省略号(...)\n   - 提供\"更多\"按钮(点击触发`onShowMore`回调)\n3. 响应式调整：当包含该组件的表格或容器大小改变时，会自动重新计算可显示的标签数量\n4. 边界情况处理：当只剩一个标签且仍无法完整显示时，对该标签进行溢出省略处理\n\n使用方法"},{"attributes":{"header":1},"insert":"\n"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"plain"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"<template>"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"  <MoreTag :list=\"tagList\" @showMore=\"handleShowMore\" />"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"</template>"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n\n"},{"insert":"<script>"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"import MoreTag from './MoreTag.vue'"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n\n"},{"insert":"export default {"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"  components: {"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"    MoreTag"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"  },"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"  data() {"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"    return {"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"      tagList: ['标签1', '标签2', '标签3', ...] // 你的标签数组"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"    }"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"  },"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"  methods: {"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"    handleShowMore() {"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"plain"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"      // 处理\"更多\"按钮点击事件"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"      console.log('显示更多标签')"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"    }"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"  }"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"}"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"</script>"},{"attributes":{"code-block":"vue"},"insert":"\n\n"},{"insert":"\nProps参数"},{"attributes":{"header":1},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"- `list` (Array): 必需，要展示的字符串标签数组，默认值为空数组 `[]`\n- `onShowMore` (Function): 可选，当点击\"更多\"按钮时触发的回调函数\n\n注意事项"},{"attributes":{"header":1},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"1. 组件内部会自动处理标签溢出逻辑，无需手动干预\n2. 当容器大小变化时(如表格列宽调整)，组件会自动重新计算\n3. 组件使用了特定的CSS类名(如`tag-btn-container`, `tag-list-container`等)，需要确保对应的样式文件(`table-tag-list.scss`)被正确引入\n\n内部实现细节"},{"attributes":{"header":1},"insert":"\n"},{"insert":"- 使用`$nextTick`确保DOM更新后再进行溢出计算\n- 通过深度克隆原始标签数组避免修改props\n- 在组件销毁或停用时正确清理resize监听器\n- 支持国际化，\"更多\"按钮文本使用`this.$t('更多')`获取翻译\n\n这个组件特别适合在数据表格的单元格中使用，当单元格内需要展示多个标签但空间有限时，可以提供良好的用户体验。\n"}],"extra":{"updator":"Austin","update_at":"2026-01-21 17:44:22"}}